snippet.title: Command & Conquer 3: Kane's Wrath - Nod Trailer
snippet.description: Official Single Player Trailer for Command & Conquer 3: Kane's Wrath.  Pledge your allegiance to the Brotherhood of Nod and to Kane!  Peace through power!  In Stores March 25.  Check out http://www.commandandconquer.com
